com.herocraftonline.heroes.api.events

Class ClassChangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.event.Event
      • com.herocraftonline.heroes.api.events.ClassChangeEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.event.Cancellable

    public class ClassChangeEvent
extends org.bukkit.event.Event
implements org.bukkit.event.Cancellable
    This is a cancellable event that fires whenever a hero changes from one class to another. If this event is initiated because of an admin command the cancelled state will be ignored.
